title: Ep 322 - Jethalal Proposes To Daya
shortDesc: When it's Jethalal and Daya's turn to go on the stage and proposes to each other, they are shy as Champaklal is sitting in the audience. Once they get a thumbs up from him, there is no holding back.

title: Ep 323 - Komal And Dr. Hathis Love Story
shortDesc: Komal shares her and Dr. Hathi's love story. She describes how food was one of the reasons for them to get together and it still holds them together.

title: Ep 324 - Popatlals Speech On Valentines Day
shortDesc: After all the couples are done expressing their love for their spouses, Popatlal takes over the stage and expresses his sorrow as he does not have anyone to be with on Valentine's Day.

title: Ep 325 - Daya Wants To Go To Goa
shortDesc: Daya receives a call from her friend Bharti who has planned a trip to Goa with her family. She insists Daya accompany them on the trip. Will Daya be able to convince Jethalal?

title: Ep 326 - Bhide Is Angry At Tappu
shortDesc: Seeing all the children from Tappu Sena already play Holi, he scolds all of them and asks them to go home. Helpless, they go to Taarak for help. Will Taarak be able to help them?

title: Ep 327 - Iyers Mater Plan
shortDesc: Iyer comes to Jetha's house and tells Daya that he is planning to take Babita to Mahabaleshwar on Holi. He also asks Daya to not disclose this as he wants to give Babita a surprise.

title: Ep 328 - Jethalal Is On Cloud Nine
shortDesc: As soon as Jethalal comes to know that Iyer is taking Babita to Mahabaleshwar, he cannot keep calm. He plans to surprise Babita by planning a trip to the same destination with his entire family.

title: Ep 329 - No More A Secret
shortDesc: All the ladies of Goduldham society come to visit Daya to decide the menu for Holi. Daya looks muddled every time they talk about Holi leaving them suspicious.

title: Ep 330 - Jethalal Gets The Shock Of His Life
shortDesc: As soon as Jethalal sees Babita standing in her balcony, he gets stunned. Heartbroken, he curses himself and acts like he is going to faint. Will he be able to cancel the trip and stay back?

title: Ep 331 - Daya Restricts Jethalal From Playing Holi
shortDesc: While everyone is enjoying the festival of colours, Daya restricts Jethalal from playing Holi as he is not well. She locks him on the balcony and he helplessly watches everyone enjoy.

title: Ep 332 - Champaklal Cannot Fall Asleep
shortDesc: While everyone is fast asleep, Champaklal is unable to fall asleep. As he goes out to stand on the balcony, he sees a man who starts running as soon as Champaklal asks him his whereabouts. Who is the man?

title: Ep 333 - Security Measures
shortDesc: To ensure that no unknown person or thief enters the society, Bhide gets the entire society's compound fenced. Later, as Madhavi is away, other ladies offer Bhide to have his lunch with them.

title: Ep 334 - Everyone Appreciates Bhide
shortDesc: Seeing the society properly fenced, everyone appreciates Bhide for getting the work done so fast. When Iyer criticizes him saying there is no gate at the entrance, Popatlal supports Bhide which shuts Iyer's mouth.

title: Ep 335 - Another Crisis At Gokuldham
shortDesc: Everyone in the society is tensed as they find a truck stuck in the society's entrance. As nobody is able to move out because of the fencing, Tappu comes up with an idea which everyone disapproves of.

title: Ep 336 - Jethalal Flirts With Babita
shortDesc: Jethalal tells Babita that she has been looking a bit different from past few days only after which she tells him that she has gotten a haircut. Listening to this, Daya expresses her wish to get a similar haircut.
